                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18181028-78-off450 t18181028-78-cd451"></join>, two aprons, value 1s.; three table-cloths, value 2s.; one gown, value 2s.; two pillow-cases, value 6d.; one shirt, value 1s.; two handkerchiefs, value 4d.; one shift, value 1s.; one night-gown, value 6d.; two neck-handkerchiefs, value 1s., and one pinafore, value 2d.
